reviewText: CANTINFLAS PLAYS A DRAMA FORIEGN FILM AS A ELEMENTARY SCHOOL TEACHER AND HE DID A GOOD ONE. I ENJOY THIS FILM.

I like the move and that is one of the reasons why I bought it. I'm a Spanish teacher and I wanted to show it to my students. But unfortunately, it did not have subtitles. I was really disappointed on that. Other than that, the movie was great. I recommend it.

its not the sellers fault, but this movie is so old and hasn't been remade into better quality. so i didn't even finish watching it the first time i put it on. but i had no issues w/seller at all. they were great
